    <title>The Impact of Green Energy Production on Healthiness Perceptions and Preferences</title>
    <updated>2025-04-12T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Iman Paul, Smaraki Mohanty, Jeffrey R Parker</name>
