    <title>EXPRESS: Protecting Workers from Rude Customers to Enhance Organizational Identification in Emotional Labor Environments: a Study with Call Center Agents</title>
    <updated>2025-04-02T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Hyojeong Kim, Nagesh N Murthy, Anurag Agarwal, Kwangtae Park</name>
