    <title>Die now of hunger or later of thirst: Understanding climate change adaptation decisions in vulnerable contexts</title>
    <updated>2025-04-09T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Lucrezia Nava, Jorge Chiapetti, Rui Barbosa da Rocha, Maja Tampe</name>
